assets 
=========

ralis 3.1 is using gem sprockets for this

http://railscasts.com/episodes/279-understanding-the-asset-pipeline?autoplay=true

getting all assents paths

~~~ruby
Rails.application.config.assets.paths
~~~

if you want to lead the assets one by one than call
*localhost:3000/?debug_assets=1*



~~~ruby
//=require_tree 
//=require_tree ./public
//=require_directory
~~~

